  "title": "Change event?",
  "body": "Is it possible to add a change event? So when a visitor uses a filter there should be a change event triggered? I want to give the visitor some visual feedback, like a loading button or so. The search is now too fast, visitors don't notice changes :P \n\n``` javascript\nvar onChangeHandler = function() {};\nsearch.on('change', onChangeHandler);\n```\n",
